      "message": "connection_ isn’t allowed to be nullptr, right? Let’s just make this DCHECK(connection_), or even hoist the DCHECK up into Initialize().\n\nIf connection_ is allowed to be nullptr, you should document that in the header (along with how this is expected to behave).",
